{
  "text": "that establishes the equality between the Kane-Mele index KM \u2208 Z 2 and the two-dimensional Wess-Zumino (WZ) action S WZ (w) divided by \u03c0 of the unitary-group-valued field T 2 \u220b k \u2192 w(k) \u2208 U (n). The WZ action in question is defined following Witten's prescription [CITATION_1] : one extends the field w to a U (n)-valued map W on an oriented 3-dimensional manifold B with boundary \u2202B = T 2 , demanding that W | \u2202B = w, and one sets",
